<subSubSection id="4B86EC92E826303BE2F0FA2BB9A49E2C" pageId="1" pageNumber="298" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="0323BF19E826303BE2F0FA2BB9A49E2C" blockId="1.[151,1436,601,1596]" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">
<emphasis id="31E8630BE826303BE2F0FA2BBA219DE7" bold="true" box="[199,327,1504,1527]" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named in honor of Dr. Cleide Costa, the great Brazilian entomologist who dedicated her life to the study of neotropical insect larvae and studies of Elateroidea, and in commemoration of her 
<number id="B554AD3EE826303BE658F9C9BFEC9E09" box="[1135,1162,1538,1561]" pageId="1" pageNumber="298" value="50.0">50</number>
year career in the Museu de Zoologia da Universidade de São Paulo (
<collectionCode id="658D27DCE826303BE05CF9EEB9D19E2C" box="[619,695,1573,1596]" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/9yp6-zxp9" name="Sao Paulo, Museu de Zoologia da Universidade de Sao Paulo" pageId="1" pageNumber="298">MZSP</collectionCode>
).
</paragraph>
